column7: {"Other Type": {"endIndexInSegment": 358, "startIndexInSegment": 61, "selectedText": "Our Promise to You Dallas County Community College District's (DCCCD) Privacy Commitment is based on two principles. We promise to: Comply with all the applicable local, state and federal laws and regulations; and Protect your privacy while still offering relevant, personalized service.", "value": "Introductory/Generic"}}
{"Security Measure": {"endIndexInSegment": 305, "startIndexInSegment": 285, "selectedText": "Protect your privacy", "value": "Generic"}}

{"Other Type": {"endIndexInSegment": 253, "startIndexInSegment": 0, "selectedText": "DCCCD is a public higher education institution and therefore bound by the Texas Public Information Act and the Family Education Rights and Privacy Act (FERPA). {"Other Type": {"endIndexInSegment": 309, "startIndexInSegment": 9, "selectedText": "Texas Public Information Act The Texas Public Information Act requires disclosure of information by a public body -- unless the law specifically protects the information.
